{"sections":[],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/gio\/actionprotocol"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"kind":"symbol","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO"]]},"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"metadata":{"symbolKind":"protocol","roleHeading":"Protocol","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"ActionProtocol"}],"title":"ActionProtocol","externalID":"s:3GIO14ActionProtocolP","role":"symbol","modules":[{"name":"GIO"}],"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"protocol"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"ActionProtocol","kind":"identifier"}]},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/ActionProtocol","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"abstract":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"GAction"},{"type":"text","text":" represents a single named action."}],"topicSections":[{"title":"Instance Properties","identifiers":["doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/ActionProtocol\/action_ptr-7plfn","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/ActionProtocol\/enabled","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/ActionProtocol\/name","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/ActionProtocol\/parameterType","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/ActionProtocol\/state","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/ActionProtocol\/stateHint","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/ActionProtocol\/stateType"],"generated":true,"anchor":"Instance-Properties"},{"anchor":"Instance-Methods","identifiers":["doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/ActionProtocol\/activate(parameter:)-3bdsn","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/ActionProtocol\/activate(parameter:)-5h0q3","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/ActionProtocol\/bind(property:to:_:flags:transformFrom:transformTo:)","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/ActionProtocol\/changeState(value:)","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/ActionProtocol\/get(property:)","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/ActionProtocol\/getEnabled()","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/ActionProtocol\/getName()","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/ActionProtocol\/getParameterType()","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/ActionProtocol\/getState()","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/ActionProtocol\/getStateHint()","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/ActionProtocol\/getStateType()","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/ActionProtocol\/set(property:value:)"],"generated":true,"title":"Instance Methods"}],"relationshipsSections":[{"title":"Inherits From","kind":"relationships","identifiers":["doc:\/\/GIO\/4GLib14PointerWrapperP"],"type":"inheritsFrom"},{"title":"Inherited By","identifiers":["doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/PropertyActionProtocol","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/SimpleActionProtocol"],"kind":"relationships","type":"inheritedBy"},{"title":"Conforming Types","identifiers":["doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/Action","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/ActionRef","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/PropertyAction","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/PropertyActionRef","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/SimpleAction","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/SimpleActionRef"],"kind":"relationships","type":"conformingTypes"}],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"protocol","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"ActionProtocol","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":" : "},{"text":"PointerWrapper","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:4GLib14PointerWrapperP"}],"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"type":"heading","anchor":"overview","level":2,"text":"Overview"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The main interface to an action is that it can be activated with"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"[method"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Gio.Action.activate"},{"text":"]. This results in the ‘activate’ signal being","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"emitted. An activation has a "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"GVariant"},{"type":"text","text":" parameter (which may be"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"code":"NULL","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"). The correct type for the parameter is determined by a static"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"parameter type (which is given at construction time)."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"An action may optionally have a state, in which case the state may be","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"set with [method","type":"text"},{"code":"Gio.Action.change_state","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"]. This call takes a [type[Variant](\/\/documentation\/glib\/variant]. The"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"correct type for the state is determined by a static state type","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"(which is given at construction time)."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The state may have a hint associated with it, specifying its valid"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"range."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"code":"GAction","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" is merely the interface to the concept of an action, as"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"described above.  Various implementations of actions exist, including","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"[class"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/SimpleAction"},{"text":"].","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"In all cases, the implementing class is responsible for storing the","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"name of the action, the parameter type, the enabled state, the optional"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"state type and the state and emitting the appropriate signals when these","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"change. The implementor is responsible for filtering calls to","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"[method","type":"text"},{"code":"Gio.Action.activate","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"] and [method"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Gio.Action.change_state"},{"type":"text","text":"]"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"for type safety and for the state being enabled.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Probably the only useful thing to do with a "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"GAction"},{"text":" is to put it","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"inside of a [class"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/SimpleActionGroup","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":"]."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/ActionProtocol","isActive":true},{"text":" protocol exposes the methods and properties of an underlying ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"GAction"},{"type":"text","text":" instance."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"The default implementation of these can be found in the protocol extension below.","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"For a concrete class that implements these methods and properties, see "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/Action","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Alternatively, use ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/ActionRef","isActive":true},{"text":" as a lighweight, ","type":"text"},{"code":"unowned","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" reference if you already have an instance you just want to use."}]}],"kind":"content"}],"references":{"doc://GIO/documentation/GIO/SimpleActionProtocol":{"title":"SimpleActionProtocol","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"protocol"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"SimpleActionProtocol","kind":"identifier"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"SimpleActionProtoc